descriptionHtml:
This is a package of save files. Including save files are completion of Dragon Rising, Main Quest, Main Quest + Completion of the Civil War (in two seperate files from both sides). No mods used. No cheats used. No additional locations other then those required for completion have been discovered. Character has leveled once. No perks invested. Invested 10 points in health. 5000 gold or so. Low leveled gear. No houses purchased. This is my first I hope you will like it. 

Credit to Bethesda Software for one of the greatest RPG ever made.
author: gexen2
